''' This demonstration
'''
'''
''' Connect a piezo buzzer to the port... and listen.
'''
'''
''' -------------------PORTB-----------------
''' Bit#:  -7---6---5---4---3---2---1---0---
''' PCB
''' Constants
''' SOUND --------|SND|---------------------
'''-----------------------------------------
''' -------------------PORTC-----------------
''' Bit#:  -7---6---5---4---3---2---1---0---
''' PCB    NA--A6--A5--A4--A3--A2--A1--A0---
''' Constants
''' LED    ---------------|L4 |L3 |L2 |L1 |-  where L equates to LED
'''-----------------------------------------
'''
''' Connect the switch via suitable resistors using a standard switch connection.
''' -------------------PORTE-----------------
''' Bit#:  -7---6---5---4---3---2---1---0---
''' PCB                  --A7--
''' Constants
''' SOUND ----------------|SW |--------------
'''-----------------------------------------
'''
'''
